Integration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Adds web browsing capabilities to Claude, allowing it to interact
with websites, take screenshots, and automate web tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Configuration:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
